(66, '<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;">旺企贷（</span><a href="http://www.wangqidai.com/"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;">www.wangqidai.com</span></a><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;">）系济南旺企贷旗下独立品牌，是引入国有担保机构的P2C(Peer to Company)互联网金融交易模式平台，于2014年初正式上线。旺企贷是由从业于金融、互联网行业多年的精英团队倾心倾力打造，以负责、严谨的态度和客户至上的原则创建的一个安全、诚信、透明的投融资网络借贷平台。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;">自成立以来，旺企贷立足当下，着眼未来，确定了先进的商业模式和交易结构，以沉淀信用的价值、铸造“足信则贷”的平台为目标，肩负与投资人、企业、战略合作伙伴及员工相互依存、共建共享共赢的发展使命，追求诚信、便捷、高效的投融资环境，通过优秀的互联网技术及金融资源配置能力，为几百家实体企业提供了便捷及时的投融资服务。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;">作为国内专业的P2C 互联网金融交易平台，旺企贷以支持中小微实体企业发展为宗旨，以国有控股融资性担保机构作担保，为投资者提供一个风险真实可控而收益稳健的新型投资渠道，为有着良好实体经营、能提供固定资产抵押的中小微企业提供一个直接、高效的融资桥梁。旺企贷以其诚信、透明、公平、高效、创新的经营理念，贴心为客户提供一站式服务，在业内赢得了良好口碑，已成为行业内最具影响力的品牌之一。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';line-height:1;font-size:14px;">与国有融资性担保公司达成战略合作，是旺企贷结合中国目前的投资环境所做出的明智选择。对于P2C互联网金融交易平台，尤其是投资者而言，国有融资性担保公司无疑是一道天然屏障。《道德经》中“天之道，损有余而补不足。人之道，则不然，损不足以奉有余”，旺企贷与国有融资性担保公司的强强联合，必定打造出新时代的互联网金融交易平台。</span>\r\n</p>', '', '<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 style="font-size:20px;color:#46AEE0;">\r\n	<h3 style="font-size:20px;color:#46AEE0;">\r\n		<h3 style="font-size:20px;color:#46AEE0;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;background:url(https://www.wangqidai.com/dyweb/dythemes/wqd_genesis/images/line_menu_small.png) -1px 100% no-repeat #F3F3F3;">\r\n			管理团队\r\n		</h3>\r\n		<div class="au_item" style="margin:0px;padding:5px 5px 5px 35px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#444444;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n			<p>\r\n				<img src="https://www.wangqidai.com/dyupfiles/images/2014-11/27/20141127103514_64974.jpg" width="120" height="169" align="left" alt="" /><strong><span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;李亚鹏</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;执行总裁</strong></span></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;3年华尔街投行经验,&nbsp;2007</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">年回国创业，</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">5</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">年中国中小企业金融服务经验</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;曾作为主要人员服务于国内领先的国有担保公司，并设立了公司的批</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">量化、标准化方案设计</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;和风险防控体系。</span><span style="font-size:14px;">为新金融时代互联网金融的巨大潜力所吸引，于2014</span><span style="font-size:14px;">年，创立旺企贷。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;李亚鹏先生拥有美国匹兹堡大学和西安石油大学双学士学位。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<img src="https://www.wangqidai.com/dyupfiles/images/2014-12/23/20141223130819_88447.jpg" width="120" height="169" align="left" alt="" />&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;</strong><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"><strong>黄剑敏&nbsp;</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>执行副总裁</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;毕业于中国人民大学，大数据及互联网营销专家，拥有8年互联网技术和运营经验，在互联网</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;金融领域拥有丰富的全流程实操经验。先后就职于百度、搜狗等知名互联网企业。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;2013年，在O2O领域创业，对垂直搜索类互联网产品有着丰富的产品设计、运营实战经验。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;2014年，参与创办旺企贷。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<img src="https://www.wangqidai.com/dyupfiles/images/2014-11/27/20141127103710_41761.jpg" width="120" height="169" align="left" alt="" /><strong>&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;"><span>师耀飞</span></span></strong>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style="font-size:14px;">风险管理部总监</span></strong>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;5年金融从业经验。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;先后就职于黑石投资、民生银行，任高级业务经理负责中小微企业贷款业务</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">擅长把控企业</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;风险，灵活管理信贷额度，</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">致力于用互联网补充传统金融。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;2014年加入旺企贷，负责中</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">小微借款企业风险管理和金融理</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp;财产品的创新。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<img src="https://www.wangqidai.com/dyupfiles/images/2014-11/27/20141127103914_80121.jpg" width="120" height="169" align="left" alt="" />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;张丽娜</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;数据分析部总监</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;4年互联网金融信息分析经验。</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;先后就职于新东方科技教育集团、搜狐、中国人寿，负责金融数据的收集与分析。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;">专注于互联网金融发展，</span><span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">2014年加入旺企贷，主要负责研究网贷市场，预测市场发展变化趋</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;势，提供投资策略和建议，为公司投资和发展提供全方位的规划与分析。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;张丽娜女士拥有北京工业大学数学硕士学位。&nbsp;</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;"><br />\r\n</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<img src="https://www.wangqidai.com/dyupfiles/images/2014-11/27/20141127104123_43605.jpg" width="120" height="169" align="left" alt="" /><strong><span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;胡显峰</span><span style="font-size:14px;"></span></strong>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;产品运营部总监</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;5年互联网产品设计经验。</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;对互联网金融及电子商务等方向有充分的经验和想法。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;先后就职于ATOS、江南科友、尚品网、民生银行信用卡商城，任产品经理负责相关互联网项</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;目的设计与架构。</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">致力于用互联网改变世界，2014年加入旺企贷，负责公司产品运营部门整</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">体架构和主产品设计。</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">胡显峰先生拥有东北师范大学软件工程学士学位。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<img src="https://www.wangqidai.com/dyupfiles/images/2014-12/02/20141202165046_73927.jpg" width="120" height="169" align="left" alt="" />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;范俊伟&nbsp;</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>技术研发部总监</strong><strong></strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p16">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;7年互联网产品及研发经验。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p16">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;对互联网及移动互联网的产品研发有充分的了解。</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">钻研互联网安</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">全领域，对资金安全有深入</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p16">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp;研究。</span><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">加入旺企贷后，主要负责产品的技术架构、设计及维护。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p16">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;范俊伟先生拥有华北电力大学学士学位。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;"></span>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<br />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<img src="https://www.wangqidai.com/dyupfiles/images/2014-12/23/20141223162704_16669.jpg" width="120" height="169" align="left" alt="" />\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;厉东</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<span style="line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;营销部总监</strong></span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;6年互联网产品营销经验。</span><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;先后就职于四通集团、苏宁电器，负责市场营销战略部署与大数据分析策略。</span><span style="font-size:14px;">长期专注于互联</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;网营销领域，对互联网营销现状和发展趋势有全面的深入认知与理解，独到的创意取得丰厚的</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;互联网营销硕果，曾参与加多宝、联想、海尔、中国移动等互联网整合营销项目。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n			<p class="p0">\r\n				<span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;2014年正式加入旺企贷担任营销部总监，全面负责企业品牌形象及营销战略工作。</span>\r\n			</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n<br />\r\n	</h3>\r\n</h3>', NULL, '<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size:14px;">信息部</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:14px;">媒体投放、商务合作、信息推广请联系：</span><span style="font-size:14px;"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="line-height:28px;"><strong><span><span style="font-size:14px;">电话</span><span style="font-size:14px;">：</span></span></strong></span><span style="line-height:28px;"><strong><span></span></strong><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:14px;">400-876-8855</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="line-height:28px;font-size:14px;"><strong>邮箱：</strong></span><span style="line-height:28px;"><strong><span></span></strong><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:14px;color:#337FE5;">information@wangqidai.com</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="line-height:28px;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:14px;color:#337FE5;"><br />\r\n</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-size:14px;">市场部</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="color:#444444;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', 微软雅黑, ''Microsoft Sans Serif'', tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#F3F3F3;">\r\n	<span style="line-h